{"type": "article", "id": 49389, "title": "H&M 任命全球“多样性与包容性领导者”，以及，Off-White 在东京开定制快闪店 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-01-19T04:00:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 4999, "name": "三宅一生"}, {"id": 3133, "name": "Jil Sander"}, {"id": 2211, "name": "Tod's"}, {"id": 43320, "name": "Off-White"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/201801191149272YH6q91sgmfeWMb7.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/news/h-and-m-diversity-leader-racist-advert-controversy-advertising-180118\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>H&amp;M 任命全球“多样性与包容性领导者”，以回应种族歧视事件</strong></a> | 为回应“丛林中最酷的猴子”之后的一系列事件，深陷舆论漩涡的 H&amp;M 正式任命 Annie Wu 为全球“多样性与包容性”领导者，推动该领域的工作发展。</p><p><a href=\"https://cn.reuters.com/article/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AA%E8%82%A1%EF%BC%9ATapestry%E5%B0%86%E4%BA%8E3%E6%9C%882%E6%97%A5%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%8C1%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E4%B9%B0%E5%8D%96-idCNL3S1PD3ZL\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Coach 母公司将于 3 月 2 日撤回香港上市 </strong></a>| 据路透社报道，Coach 的母公司 Tapestry 集团周四称，香港联交所已经批准在 3 月 2 日撤回上市地位，并于 1 月 30 日收市后停止买卖。此前，Tapestry 向香港联交所申请摘牌，原因是交投量偏低，拟将资源集中在纽约证交所。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>1 月 24 日至 2 月 6 日，<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/off-white-tokyo-customization-pop-up/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Off-White</a> 将在东京新宿的伊势丹开设快闪店，这家店将提供定制服务。如果你正好在东京，不要错过它。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119114742ybM4TUBneOwoCDGA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Kendall Jenner 和意大利芭蕾舞者 Roberto Bolle 代言了<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-01-18/tods-kendalljenner/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Tod’s</a>，最新广告大片描绘了两人共同度过的轻松一天，还挺自然的。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119114705DCEthlI8rfFgkWvJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.669697\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119114704wkzS1dypR8Ynu0A3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.669697\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119114704fBvDLYPEriqaReVU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801191147077X1e296KPvlhJdmN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119114708hqyAk6IUExR1M3ZO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801191147061ly4TfuCiPR8cB5H.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.669697\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119114708p47xeKsWq2jCN8dy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119114709ekyBAol7madhXftV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119114709PoZOnxYfelmJ3Wq4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.669697\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801191147103S7EURzBmIi4TAFN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.669697\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119114710EyTY8mij2qh1b3V7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.248485\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119114711v4TOyHz2QMu6iReS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180119114712YeCAt7bnBPjSkVaR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801191147123cB7K9